How to create a new rails folder?
1. rails new "Folder name"
2. Go to Gemfile and comment out two lines namely:
    gem 'spring'
    gem 'spring-watcher-listen', '~>2.0.0'
3. Then run bundle update

How to generate any model
rails generate model [model name] name:string email:string

How to add a new column to a database in rails?(in snake casing)
rails generate migration add_password_digest_to_users password_digest:string

How to remove a column to a dabase in rails?(in camel casing)
rails generate migration RemovePartNumberFromProducts part_number:string

Both snake casing and camel casing works

How to see columns of a database?
[database name].column_names
